SQL_STMT_U.val:
SELECT 仕入金額 = SUM(CASE WHEN TDT.取引Ｄ区分=3 THEN TDT.金額 ELSE 0 END) ,支払金額 = SUM(CASE WHEN TDT.取引Ｄ区分=4 THEN TDT.金額 ELSE 0 END) FROM 取引データ TDT
WHERE TDT.取引部門=:1 AND TDT.取引Ｄ区分 IN(3,4) AND (TDT.取引先Ｃ=:2 OR TDT.請求支払先Ｃ=:2) AND TDT.伝票日付 BETWEEN ':3' AND ':4'
